(1, 1, '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Hello world!', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world__trashed', '', '', '2019-03-14 13:26:24', '2019-03-14 13:26:24', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2, 1, '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Please contact us via the details below and we will get back to you. Please include your name, email, contact number, a brief description of service required and your preferred method of contact. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Email: stephanie@whitetreehr.co.uk</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Phone: 07833492482</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Contact', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2019-03-14 11:00:03', '2019-03-14 11:00:03', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?page_id=2', 1, 'page', '', 0),
(3, 1, '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '<!-- wp:heading --><h2>Who we are</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Our website address is: http://whitetree.localhost.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>What personal data we collect and why we collect it</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Comments</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>An anonymised string created from your e-mail address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service Privacy Policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Media</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Contact forms</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Cookies</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt in to saving your name, e-mail address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you have an account and you log in to this site, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Embedded content from other websites</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Analytics</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Who we share your data with</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>How long we retain your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognise and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>What rights you have over your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Where we send your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Your contact information</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Additional information</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>How we protect your data</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>What data breach procedures we have in place</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>What third parties we receive data from</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>What automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data</h3><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><h3>Industry regulatory disclosure requirements</h3><!-- /wp:heading -->', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'open', '', 'privacy-policy', '', '', '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '2019-03-05 20:52:15', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?page_id=3', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(5, 1, '2019-03-07 11:10:34', '2019-03-07 11:10:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your Strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day Operational HR, WhiteTree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Operational HR</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Assisting your businesses with day to day HR management. Operational HR areas that we cover include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employment Law </li><li>Employee Relations</li><li>Absence Management </li><li>Recruitment and Resourcing  </li><li>Performance and Appraisals </li><li>Policies and Procedures </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Strategic HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We work with your business, the management team and key stakeholders to deliver innovative, bespoke and diligent Strategic HR services that include: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Talent Management </li><li>Mergers and Acquisitions (Inc. TUPE) </li><li>Organisational Structure </li><li>Employee Engagement and Retention</li><li>Reward Management</li><li>Management Development</li><li>Restructures and Redundancy </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Project HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR are perfectly positioned to collaborate with businesses on HR projects, working with you from the initial concept to completion and implementation. We can also review, analyse and improve existing projects or aid development of ongoing projects within your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create bespoke HR projects</li><li>Aid businesses in the completion of projects </li><li>Review, analyse, improve existing projects or compliment the development of ongoing projects </li><li>Project integration </li><li>Project documentation </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Systems, Data Analysis and Management Information</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTreeHR are specialists in HR Software and the management of employee data, as well as Employee Self portals. We are able to help with all of your HR Management Information and reporting needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>HR Software Integration, Management, Maintenance</li><li>Employee Information Management and Storage </li><li>Key Performance Indicators (KPIâs) </li><li>Management Information (MI) </li><li>Data Analysis and Reporting </li><li>Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Annual reporting packages </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are HR Administration experts here at WhiteTree HR. We work with you and your business to alleviate this time consuming, yet integral part of HR so that your time is freed to focus on business essentials without having the worry of everyday necessities. Some of the HR Administration areas we cover are:  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and Procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data Entry </li><li>Document Management </li><li>Recruitment Administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li><li>Yearly policy updates </li><li>Legal compliance </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Health Check</strong> <strong>and HR Audit</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our free HR Health Check provides you with an initial indication as to where you are with meeting HR standards and regulations, highlighting any potential risk.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Following on from WhiteTree\'s HR Health Check, our HR Audit provides you with an independent, objective, impartial review of your policies and procedures. This enables you to highlight and mitigate any risk, reduce cost, improve and drive performance through your people, ultimately adding value to your organisation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Further to this we can provide employment legislation, government updates and we will review and assess your current policies and procedures and report back to you clearly highlighting any areas of improvement, potential exposure, legal compliance and actions you can take. Our approach is always bespoke to fit the needs of your dynamic business and we tailor our solutions packages allowing you to pick and mix to meet your exact requirements.&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Our free HR Health Check provides an initial guide to where you are with your HR requirements </li><li>Further to this we can ensure that you are up to date with current employment legislation and are legally compliant with a review of your current policies and procedures with a clear and detailed report of recommendations </li><li>Action plans provided </li><li>Policies, procedures, terms and conditions along with employee handbooks are available from WhiteTreeHR </li><li>Annual updates as and when legal changes come into place along with any changes in employment legislations to ensure that you stay compliant </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Take our free HR Health Check questionnaire to help you understand how healthy your HR is today!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2019-03-14 12:48:36', '2019-03-14 12:48:36', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?page_id=5', -2, 'page', '', 0),
(6, 1, '2019-03-07 11:10:34', '2019-03-07 11:10:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are my services </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-07 11:10:34', '2019-03-07 11:10:34', '', 5, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/07/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
