(20, 1, '2019-03-07 11:54:58', '2019-03-07 11:54:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606266\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606266\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a selection of packages to suit our clients needs. We aim to be bespoke, affordable, innovative and conscientious of our clients business needs and requirements. We have detailed our most popular packages but are completely flexible in our approach, as experience tells us, no single business is the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Bamboo Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âpay as you goâ package for ultimate flexibility, whether it be by the hour or day. Discounts are offered for multiple and regular requirements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Oak Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âretentionâ package for stability and a guaranteed set service. Perfect for businesses that require a fixed number of hours, days or onsite visits per week/month/year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Juniper Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âOnsiteâ visits package. Great if you need or prefer a face to face HR presence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Aspen Package</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âProject HRâ package. Ideal for your business if you have a specific HR project that you would like to create, transform, implement or integrate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Elder Tree Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Systems, Data and Management Information (HRMI)â package. Suitable for any business that requires requires regular or ad hoc data analysis, statistics and reports. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Maple Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Auditâ Package. For businesses that would like their current HR processes and documentation reviewing with advice provided on current legal compliance and any suggested amendments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Birch Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âEssential HRâ package provides you with the HR foundations for your business, including Terms and Conditions and Employee Handbook. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><a href=\"http://whitetree.localhost/contact\">Contact us</a> for your Free Consultation today!  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our packages serve as a guide. We are a bespoke HR Consultancy and will work with you to provide the right HR support for you and your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Packages', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'packages', '', '', '2019-03-25 14:28:33', '2019-03-25 14:28:33', '', 0, 'http://whitetree.localhost/?page_id=20', -1, 'page', '', 0),
(21, 1, '2019-03-07 11:54:58', '2019-03-07 11:54:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Packages</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR offer a selection of packages to suit our clients needs. We aim to be bespoke, affordable, innovative and conscientious of our clients business needs and requirements. We have detailed our most popular packages but are completely flexible in our approach as experience tells us, no single business is the same. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact us today for a free consultation to\ndiscuss how we can help you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hourly </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer an hourly rate, usually purchased in\nblocks of 4. Discounts for multiple and regular&nbsp;\nblocks purchased </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Daily </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using the same principal as our hourly rate. We offer discount for multiple and regular days and we have options for onsite visits as well as remote. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pay as you go â hourly and daily </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Hourly and Daily rates are available on a\npay as you go basis, specifically with our Small â Medium business client in mind.\nThis enables them to be more flexible and have the same HR Support without\ncommitting to a set plan or cost.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Project</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We can offer fixed price quotes for bespoke\nprojects. Please get on contact with us today to see how we can help. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HR Management Information Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you require MI information every month,\nevery quarter, annually or even a one off report, then we have packages to suit\nyour needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Annual HR Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You receive a set number of remote HR support hours,\nhowever many suits your business requirements, along with legal updates\nthroughout the year to ensure that you are working with the most up to date and\nrecent employment legislation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HR Audit Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR will review your current HR\npolicies and procedures and provide you with a detailed, clear report of\nsuggested improvements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Essential HR Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This package contains your HR essentials. You and\nprocedures your company requires as well as a template offer letter and terms\nand conditions. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pick and Mix </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please contact us for a free consultation if\nyou are interested in more than one of the packages above. We are a bespoke HR\nConsultancy and will work with you to provide you with the right HR support for\nyour business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Packages', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-07 11:54:58', '2019-03-07 11:54:58', '', 20, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/07/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
