(90, 1, '2019-03-14 10:48:19', '2019-03-14 10:48:19', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR are a innovative, dynamic and diligent HR Consultancy. We pride ourselves on being flexible, bespoke and reliable enabling us to deliver premium HR solutions that work for you and your business. &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux. Stephanie has 12 years experience working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups, SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to small local businesses. During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within organisations at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides Business Managers, Key Stakeholders and Executives with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-14 10:48:19', '2019-03-14 10:48:19', '', 10, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/14/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
