(97, 1, '2019-03-14 12:48:33', '2019-03-14 12:48:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your Strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day Operational HR, WhiteTree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Operational HR</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Assisting your businesses with day to day HR management. Operational HR areas that we cover include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employment Law </li><li>Employee Relations</li><li>Absence Management </li><li>Recruitment and Resourcing  </li><li>Performance and Appraisals </li><li>Policies and Procedures </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Strategic HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We work with your business, the management team and key stakeholders to deliver innovative, bespoke and diligent Strategic HR services that include: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Talent Management </li><li>Mergers and Acquisitions (Inc. TUPE) </li><li>Organisational Structure </li><li>Employee Engagement and Retention</li><li>Reward Management</li><li>Management Development</li><li>Restructures and Redundancy </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Project HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR are perfectly positioned to collaborate with businesses on HR projects, working with you from the initial concept to completion and implementation. We can also review, analyse and improve existing projects or aid development of ongoing projects within your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create bespoke HR projects</li><li>Aid businesses in the completion of projects </li><li>Review, analyse, improve existing projects or compliment the development of ongoing projects </li><li>Project integration </li><li>Project documentation </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Systems, Data Analysis and Management Information</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTreeHR are specialists in HR Software and the management of employee data, as well as Employee Self portals. We are able to help with all of your HR Management Information and reporting needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>HR Software Integration, Management, Maintenance</li><li>Employee Information Management and Storage </li><li>Key Performance Indicators (KPIâs) </li><li>Management Information (MI) </li><li>Data Analysis and Reporting </li><li>Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Annual reporting packages </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are HR Administration experts here at WhiteTree HR. We work with you and your business to alleviate this time consuming, yet integral part of HR so that your time is freed to focus on business essentials without having the worry of everyday necessities. Some of the HR Administration areas we cover are:  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and Procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data Entry </li><li>Document Management </li><li>Recruitment Administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li><li>Yearly policy updates </li><li>Legal compliance </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Health Check</strong> <strong>and HR Audit</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our free HR Health Check provides you with an initial indication as to where you are with meeting HR standards and regulations, highlighting any potential risk.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Following on from WhiteTree\'s HR Health Check, our HR Audit provides you with an independent, objective, impartial review of your policies and procedures. This enables you to highlight and mitigate any risk, reduce cost, improve and drive performance through your people, ultimately adding value to your organisation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Further to this we can provide employment legislation, government updates and we will review and assess your current policies and procedures and report back to you clearly highlighting any areas of improvement, potential exposure, legal compliance and actions you can take. Our approach is always bespoke to fit the needs of your dynamic business and we tailor our solutions packages allowing you to pick and mix to meet your exact requirements.&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Our free HR Health Check provides an initial guide to where you are with your HR requirements </li><li>Further to this we can ensure that you are up to date with current employment legislation and are legally compliant with a review of your current policies and procedures with a clear and detailed report of recommendations </li><li>Action plans provided </li><li>Policies, procedures, terms and conditions along with employee handbooks are available from WhiteTreeHR </li><li>Annual updates as and when legal changes come into place along with any changes in employment legislations to ensure that you stay compliant </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Take our free HR Health Check questionnaire to help you understand how healthy your HR is today!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-14 12:48:33', '2019-03-14 12:48:33', '', 5, 'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/14/5-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
